Package com.arkoisystems.arkoicompiler.stage.syntaxAnalyzer.parser.types

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnnotationParser
    A AbstractParser for the AnnotationSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the AnnotationSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken is capable to parse the AnnotationSyntaxAST.
    ArgumentDefinitionParser
    A AbstractParser for the ArgumentDefinitionSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the ArgumentDefinitionSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken is capable to parse the ArgumentDefinitionSyntaxAST.
    BlockParser
    A AbstractParser for the BlockSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the BlockSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken is capable to parse the BlockSyntaxAST.
    ExpressionParser
    A AbstractParser for the ExpressionSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the ExpressionSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken is capable to parse the ExpressionSyntaxAST.
    FunctionParser
    A AbstractParser for the FunctionDefinitionSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the FunctionDefinitionSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken is capable to parse the FunctionDefinitionSyntaxAST.
    OperableParser
    A AbstractParser for the AbstractOperableSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the AbstractOperableSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken and is capable to parse a new AbstractStatementSyntaxAST.
    StatementParser
    A AbstractParser for the AbstractStatementSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the AbstractStatementSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken and parent AbstractSyntaxAST are capable to parse a new AbstractStatementSyntaxAST.
    TypeParser
    A AbstractParser for the TypeSyntaxAST with which you can easily parse the TypeSyntaxAST or check if the current AbstractToken is capable to parse the TypeSyntaxAST.
